    Annotation Type Description
    ChangeEffect
    Annotation used for generating ServiceProfile.
    ChangeEffects
    Annotation used for aggregating @ChangeEffect annotation For each of such annotation a separate addChangeEffect call is made on SimpleAPIService.

    OntologyClasses
    Annotation which is used for Ontology registering.
    Output
    Annotation used for generating ServiceProfile.
